table_description: Groups in the Google Workspace domain.

columns.name: id
columns.description: The unique ID of the group.

columns.name: email
columns.description: The email address of the group.

columns.name: adminCreated
columns.description: Indicates if the group was created by an admin.

columns.name: directMembersCount
columns.description: The number of direct members in the group.

columns.name: aliases
columns.description: List of email aliases associated with the group.

columns.name: nonEditableAliases
columns.description: List of email aliases that cannot be edited.
